assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n傳熱非常快同均勻 買返黎用左兩晚 已經形成左好靚既防黏層<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n反光好好 亦都做到防黏 最好既係開鍋個時唔駛太多心機 已經均勻咁成個pan都形成防黏層<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但係唔好既地方呢 係佢好貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acb4501610e9ecc78a76e462c821eb63333cadd4","tid":1997422,"uid":175025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T16:20:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4OWqCWe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4OWqCWe.jpg&h=f1c33b9a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n開鍋之後個樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d95067d42c725845af49a749842148058005c2f8","tid":1997422,"uid":182683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"acb4501610e9ecc78a76e462c821eb63333cadd4","tid":1997422,"uid":175025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T16:20:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4OWqCWe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4OWqCWe.jpg&h=f1c33b9a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n開鍋之後個樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T17:31:42.000Z","msg":"上面d圖靚咁多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nBtw幾錢 有興趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5f326440fd148e47bf7d6c099f73390b4eef9a4","tid":1997422,"uid":182683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d95067d42c725845af49a749842148058005c2f8","tid":1997422,"uid":182683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"acb4501610e9ecc78a76e462c821eb63333cadd4","tid":1997422,"uid":175025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T16:20:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4OWqCWe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\